# Reusable components (Kowju)

Before adding new primitives or one-off markup for a section, **search this project** under `app/components/` and **reuse** these first. If something is missing, add a **small, named** component here and append a short entry below.

## Layout & structure

| Component | Path | Role |
|-----------|------|------|
| **Container** | `base/Container.vue` | Centers content; `max-w-5xl` + horizontal padding. Wrap section inner content when a max width is needed. |
| **Section** | `base/Section.vue` | Semantic `<section>` with optional `id`, optional `title` (renders `h2`), scroll-margin, optional `enter` (motion). Slots: `intro`, default. Use for page sections instead of raw `<section>` when this pattern fits. |
| **BaseStack** | `base/BaseStack.vue` | Vertical rhythm primitive for child spacing. Variants: `tight`, `default`, `loose`, `comfortable`. |
| **BaseGrid** | `base/BaseGrid.vue` | Grid rhythm primitive with token-backed spacing. Variants: `compact`, `default`, `comfortable` (plus optional axis-specific gaps). |

## Typography & headings

| Component | Path | Role |
|-----------|------|------|
| **BasePageHeader** | `base/BasePageHeader.vue` | Page hero title: `title` or default slot, optional `lead`, `align` (`left` \| `center` \| `right`), `headingLevel` (`1` \| `2`). |
| **BaseSectionHeader** | `base/BaseSectionHeader.vue` | Section title block: optional `overline` + `BaseOverline`, `title` or default slot, optional `lead` (or `#lead` slot), `align`, `dividers` on overline, `headingLevel` (`2` \| `3` \| `4`). Slot `overline` for custom overline content. |
| **BaseOverline** | `base/BaseOverline.vue` | Small uppercase label (brand). Props: `dividers` (line decorations). Prefer via **BaseSectionHeader** unless used alone. |

## Actions & links

| Component | Path | Role |
|-----------|------|------|
| **BaseButton** | `base/BaseButton.vue` | Default CTA: wraps **BaseButtonPrimary** (PrimeVue `Button`). Slot = label/content. |
| **BaseButtonPrimary** | `base/BaseButtonPrimary.vue` | Primary filled button (default emphasis). |
| **BaseButtonSecondary** | `base/BaseButtonSecondary.vue` | Secondary severity button. |
| **BaseButtonOutlined** | `base/BaseButtonOutlined.vue` | Outlined button. |
| **BaseButtonOnBrandPrimary** | `base/BaseButtonOnBrandPrimary.vue` | Filled CTA on **`bg-brand-900`**: gold surface + brand text (`Button` **`unstyled`**, classes in **`utils/button-on-brand-classes`**). |
| **BaseButtonOnBrandSecondary** | `base/BaseButtonOnBrandSecondary.vue` | Ghost / outline CTA on **`bg-brand-900`**: gold border + light gold label, hover **`brand-800`** fill. Pair with **OnBrandPrimary**. |
| **BaseLinkText** | `base/BaseLinkText.vue` | Text link with trailing icon. Props: `to`, `label` (default `"Learn more"`), `as` (`link` | `text`), `trailingIcon` (`arrow` \| `download`), `external`, `tone` (`default` \| `inverse` for `bg-brand-900`). |
| **BaseGalleryLightbox** | `base/BaseGalleryLightbox.vue` | Full-screen PrimeVue `Drawer` + `Galleria` with thumbnails: `images` (`src`, `alt`, optional `width`/`height`), `v-model:visible`, optional `drawerId` (for `aria-controls`), optional `startIndex`. |

